ccessdate=August 16, 2017|work=The Hollywood Reporter|date=August 10, 2017|language=en}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"OyelowoCast\">{{cite news|url=https://deadline.com/2017/08/david-oyelowo-chaos-walking-tom-holland-daisy-ridley-doug-liman-sci-fi-movie-lionsgate-1202153953/|title=David Oyelowo Steps Into 'Chaos Walking' For Lionsgate, Director Doug Liman|last=Busch|first=Anita|date=August 23, 2017|website=Deadline Hollywood|access-date=August 23, 2017|language=en-US}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"ErivoCast\">{{cite news|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/cynthia-erivo-joins-daisy-ridley-chaos-walking-1036386|title=Cynthia Erivo Joins Daisy Ridley in 'Chaos Walking' (Exclusive)|last=Galuppo|first=Mia|accessdate=September 7, 2017|work=The Hollywood Reporter|date=October 3, 2017|language=en-US}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"OscarCast\">{{cite news|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/oscar-jaenada-joins-doug-limans-chaos-walking-1045281|title=Oscar Jaenada Joins Doug Liman's 'Chaos Walking' (Exclusive)|last=Galuppo|first=Mia|accessdate=October 4, 2017|work=The Hollywood Reporter|date=October 3, 2017|language=en-US}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"LimanInterview\">{{cite news|last1=Evry|first1=Max|title=CS Interview: Doug Liman Talks The Wall & Chaos Walking|url=https://www.comingsoon.net/movies/features/879425-cs-interview-doug-liman-talks-the-wall-chaos-walking|accessdate=August 16, 2017|work=ComingSoon.net|date=August 15, 2017}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"ShootDate\">{{Cite web|url=http://omegaunderground.com/2017/07/30/confirmed-doug-limans-chaos-walking-begins-shooting-august-montreal/|title=CONFIRMED: Doug Liman's 'Chaos Walking' Begins Shooting This August In Montreal|last=Marc|first=Christopher|date=July 30, 2017|website=Omega Underground|access-date=August 14, 2017|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170814035517/http://omegaunderground.com/2017/07/30/confirmed-doug-limans-chaos-walking-begins-shooting-august-montreal/|archive-date=August 14, 2017|url-status=dead}}<